    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a lash of lightning energy that strikes at one creature of your choice that you can see within 15 feet of you. The target must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pulled up to 10 feet in a straight line toward you and then take [[/damage 1d8 lightning]] damage if it is within 5 feet of you.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);color:rgb(207, 210, 218);font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;font-size:14.625px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(37, 40, 48);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">Cantrip Upgrade.\u00c2\u00a0</strong></span>This spell's range and pull distance are increased by an additional 5 feet and damage increases by 1d8 when you reach levels 5 ([[/damage 2d8 lightning]], 20 foot range, 15 foot pull), 11 ([[/damage 3d8 lightning]], 25 foot range, 20 foot pull), and 17 ([[/damage 4d8 lightning]], 30 foot range, 25 foot pull).</p>",
